card.name: Distribution count transaction by Turnover EUR - Duplicate

native.query:
WITH tr as (select date_trunc({{granularity}}, TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT) as dt
     , CASE
         WHEN TURNOVER_EUR <= 50 THEN '0-50 EUR'
         WHEN TURNOVER_EUR <= 100 THEN '50-100 EUR'
         WHEN TURNOVER_EUR <= 200 THEN '100-200 EUR'
         WHEN TURNOVER_EUR <= 300 THEN '200-300 EUR'
         WHEN TURNOVER_EUR <= 400 THEN '300-400 EUR'
         WHEN TURNOVER_EUR <= 600 THEN '400-600 EUR'
         WHEN TURNOVER_EUR <= 800 THEN '600-800 EUR'
         WHEN TURNOVER_EUR <= 1000 THEN '800-1000 EUR'
         WHEN TURNOVER_EUR <= 1200 THEN '1000-1200 EUR'
         WHEN TURNOVER_EUR <= 1400 THEN '1200-1400 EUR'
         WHEN TURNOVER_EUR <= 1600 THEN '1400-1600 EUR'
         WHEN TURNOVER_EUR <= 1800 THEN '1600-1800 EUR'
         WHEN TURNOVER_EUR <= 2000 THEN '1800-2000 EUR'
         WHEN TURNOVER_EUR <= 5000 THEN '2000-5000 EUR'
         WHEN TURNOVER_EUR <= 10000 THEN '5000-10000 EUR'
         ELSE 'more 10000 EUR'
         END AS GROUP_SUM
     , count(1) as count_transactions
    from MART.TRANSACTIONS
    left join mart.CALCULATIONS_UNIQ on CALCULATIONS_UNIQ.TRANSACTION_ID=TRANSACTIONS.ID
where TYPE_MAIN in ('buy', 'sell') and
      CONFIRMED and
      SOURCE_MAIN = 'widget' and
      {{CREATED_AT}} and {{partner_name}} and {{widget_id}} and {{fiat_currency}} and
      {{crypto_currency}} and {{GEO_card}} and {{country_card}} and {{turnover_eur}} and
      {{network}} and {{type_operation}} and {{pay_system}} and {{ACQUIRER}} and {{Try_Again}}
group by 1,2)

select tr.dt
     , tr.GROUP_SUM
     , GROUP_SUM_TURNOVER_EUR.order_id
     , tr.count_transactions
     , tr.count_transactions/sum(tr.count_transactions) over (partition by 1) as percent
    from tr
left join ANALYST.GROUP_SUM_TURNOVER_EUR on GROUP_SUM_TURNOVER_EUR.GROUP_SUM = tr.GROUP_SUM
where {{GROUP_SUM}}
order by 3

card.name: Distribution Grouped Error by Turnover EUR - Duplicate

native.query:
WITH trans AS (
    SELECT
        DATE_TRUNC({{granularity}}, TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT) AS dt,
     CASE
         WHEN coalesce(nullifzero(TURNOVER_EUR), TRANSACTIONS.FIAT_AMOUNT_EUR) <= 50 THEN '0-50 EUR'
         WHEN coalesce(nullifzero(TURNOVER_EUR), TRANSACTIONS.FIAT_AMOUNT_EUR) <= 100 THEN '50-100 EUR'
         WHEN coalesce(nullifzero(TURNOVER_EUR), TRANSACTIONS.FIAT_AMOUNT_EUR) <= 200 THEN '100-200 EUR'
         WHEN coalesce(nullifzero(TURNOVER_EUR), TRANSACTIONS.FIAT_AMOUNT_EUR) <= 300 THEN '200-300 EUR'
         WHEN coalesce(nullifzero(TURNOVER_EUR), TRANSACTIONS.FIAT_AMOUNT_EUR) <= 400 THEN '300-400 EUR'
         WHEN coalesce(nullifzero(TURNOVER_EUR), TRANSACTIONS.FIAT_AMOUNT_EUR) <= 600 THEN '400-600 EUR'
         WHEN coalesce(nullifzero(TURNOVER_EUR), TRANSACTIONS.FIAT_AMOUNT_EUR) <= 800 THEN '600-800 EUR'
         WHEN coalesce(nullifzero(TURNOVER_EUR), TRANSACTIONS.FIAT_AMOUNT_EUR) <= 1000 THEN '800-1000 EUR'
         WHEN coalesce(nullifzero(TURNOVER_EUR), TRANSACTIONS.FIAT_AMOUNT_EUR) <= 1200 THEN '1000-1200 EUR'
         WHEN coalesce(nullifzero(TURNOVER_EUR), TRANSACTIONS.FIAT_AMOUNT_EUR) <= 1400 THEN '1200-1400 EUR'
         WHEN coalesce(nullifzero(TURNOVER_EUR), TRANSACTIONS.FIAT_AMOUNT_EUR) <= 1600 THEN '1400-1600 EUR'
         WHEN coalesce(nullifzero(TURNOVER_EUR), TRANSACTIONS.FIAT_AMOUNT_EUR) <= 1800 THEN '1600-1800 EUR'
         WHEN coalesce(nullifzero(TURNOVER_EUR), TRANSACTIONS.FIAT_AMOUNT_EUR) <= 2000 THEN '1800-2000 EUR'
         WHEN coalesce(nullifzero(TURNOVER_EUR), TRANSACTIONS.FIAT_AMOUNT_EUR) <= 5000 THEN '2000-5000 EUR'
         WHEN coalesce(nullifzero(TURNOVER_EUR), TRANSACTIONS.FIAT_AMOUNT_EUR) <= 10000 THEN '5000-10000 EUR'
         ELSE 'more 10000 EUR'
         END AS GROUP_SUM, 
        GROUP_FAILED_REASON,
        COALESCE(NULLIFZERO(TURNOVER_EUR), TRANSACTIONS.FIAT_AMOUNT_EUR) AS TURNOVER_EUR
    FROM MART.TRANSACTIONS
    left join mart.CALCULATIONS_UNIQ on CALCULATIONS_UNIQ.TRANSACTION_ID=TRANSACTIONS.ID
    WHERE TYPE_MAIN IN ('buy', 'sell')
      AND SOURCE_MAIN = 'widget'
      AND {{CREATED_AT}} AND {{partner_name}} AND {{widget_id}} AND {{fiat_currency}}
      AND {{crypto_currency}} AND {{GEO_card}} AND {{country_card}} AND {{turnover_eur}}
      AND {{network}} AND {{type_operation}} and {{pay_system}} and {{ACQUIRER}} and {{Try_Again}}
),
top_errors AS (
    SELECT GROUP_FAILED_REASON
    FROM (
        SELECT GROUP_FAILED_REASON, SUM(TURNOVER_EUR) AS total_turnover
        FROM trans
        GROUP BY GROUP_FAILED_REASON
    ) t
    ORDER BY total_turnover DESC
    LIMIT 10
)
SELECT
    trans.dt,
    -- trans.GROUP_SUM,
    trans.GROUP_FAILED_REASON, 
    SUM(trans.TURNOVER_EUR) AS total_turnover_eur
FROM trans
JOIN top_errors ON trans.GROUP_FAILED_REASON = top_errors.GROUP_FAILED_REASON
left join ANALYST.GROUP_SUM_TURNOVER_EUR on GROUP_SUM_TURNOVER_EUR.GROUP_SUM = trans.GROUP_SUM
where {{GROUP_SUM}}
GROUP BY trans.dt,
-- trans.GROUP_SUM, 
trans.GROUP_FAILED_REASON
ORDER BY trans.dt DESC
